我覺得我是一個有強迫症的人，無法接受自己車內的任何一點髒污，每當開車時看到儀表板或中控有灰塵或毛絮，都會受不了拿刷子刷掉，連老婆都有點看不下去🤣但令我最頭痛的是遮光墊上的灰塵，因為距離擋風玻璃太近，特別難清……結果！被我發現一個神器！！跟我一樣有潔癖的人注意了⚠️MAO Clean M1車用吸塵器，，搭載了6種吸頭＋延長軟管，再刁鑽的角度都沒有它做不到的，想到之前小朋友在我車內吃餅乾弄翻了整個座位或腳踏墊，以往可能要特地去找有吸塵器的自助洗或汽車美容，但這次我只靠MAO Clean M1就一次搞定了，根本不用浪費時間去處理！！集塵效果也令我非常滿意，無線的設計讓我在使用上的自由度又大大提升，廠商也很貼心的附贈一個非常有質感的收納袋，拿去當平常外出運動裝的東西也很適合👍🏼👍🏼不僅是吸塵，還有我從來沒看過的超強吹風接頭，這也是我最愛的功能之一，窗溝及後照鏡的水漬 門上的握把溝 甚至引擎室的灰塵都可以輕鬆處理，你以為只有這樣嗎？喜歡露營的我可以利用它將充氣墊充氣 木炭生火 游泳圈吹氣等等使用，根本不需要再接傳統的點菸座🎉除了車內，戶外，我在家裡也會使用，特別是衣櫃門的軌道 床頭板 工作書桌 窗溝 電視櫃這些小縫縫裡的灰塵再也逃不掉了😎▪️15kPa的超強吸力，兩段模式，最長可連續使用45分鐘▪️DC無刷馬達不衰退，延長使用壽命▪️2200mAh可抽拔式鋰電池，充電便利▪️無線設計，靈活性強▪️先蓋倒塵不沾手▪️6種吸頭，輕鬆應付各種環境▪️濾網塵桶可水洗▪️附贈質感圓桶包，收納不凌亂產品資訊 :  https://bit.ly/3gdhoji🔥濾網永久免費送活動 (註：每半年可申請一次，支付$80物流處理費，即可獲得價值$499 HEPA H13濾網棉組)@bmxmao_tw  #Bmxmao #MAOClean #M1 Nice car @ryanliuyy Handsome

先月衝動買いしたM1チップ搭載のMacBook Air💻💓インテル入ってない！新時代のやつ.°ʚ🥺ɞ°. Appleの囲み戦略にまんまとやられてるけど幸福だ🍎Officeすごい使うし周りも使うから、パソコンだけWindows派だったけど最近ではそこまで困ることもないかなと思い、、4年ぶりにMacに戻したら、iPhone、iPad、AirPodsとの組み合わせが神すぎて便利すぎて事務作業が(あんまり)面倒じゃなくなった( ᵒ̴̶̷̤◦ᵒ̴̶̷̤ ) iPhoneでコピーしたものがそのままmacでペーストできたり、 写真とかメモをいちいち送らなくても勝手に同期されている、たったそれだけのちまちましたメリットのために、15万円払うのかと葛藤していたけど、、 しかも持ってるWindows、かなりスペック(も値段も）高くてまだまだ使えるのに、←でもこの小さいことが面倒でストレスだったから解消されてストレス減ったし、全然お金出す意味あったというかもっと早く買ってればよかった←ちまちましたストレスなくなるの、すごい大事だわ、、、。あとやっぱり慣れてるから使いやすいよね結局🥺そして謎に英字キー使ってたからJISにできてハッピー( ◜︎࿀◝︎ )とはいえ、Windowsちゃんも、友達とたくさん吟味して買った大好きなパソコンなので引き続き飾っとく(使うか譲れ）💻ーーー、、、今mac衝動買いの理由思い出した←AirPods Proのマイク部分壊して、２代目買う理由を探して悩んでいたらいつの間にかmacポチってたんだったわ、、、肝心のAirPods買い換えてない←あれ？🤔𓈒𓂂𓏸#m1 #macbookair #apple #ガジェット

850i appreciation post • Before I get my driver's license I jumped in one of this icons as a passenger in a quick cruise through my town. That "quick cruise" ended as a drive it like you stole it run, drifting in some rondabouts and joints like there is no tomorrow.I completely love this car and the fact that being sideways in a BMW V12 made me feel at the top for few minutes, even with that old ass interior lol. The car itself nowadays is not a big thing but once inside it felt fast and the "low" torque was enough to do what the driver wanted to do with it, even with the open diff and, in my case, with 2 cyl not working well. Imagine how this thing goes with the whole engine running good and back in the 80's. Один из следующих проектов это легендарная BMW M1 procar. Данный автомобиль производился с 1978 по 1981 годы и создан был для того чтобы принимать участие в группе 4. Однако вскоре баварский производитель создал собственный монобренодовый чемпионат в котором принимали участие многие звёзды формулы-1 исключительно за рулем данного автомобиля оснащённого мощным двигателем в 470 л.с., который в последствии стал устанавливаться на первую BMW M5.  Соревнование проходило лишь два года. Первым победителем стал знаменитый формульный ас Ники Лауда. Кит от кампании italeri 3643  выпущеный в 2020 году. Хотя сам пластик из набора от компании ESCI из далеких 80-х. Italeri переупаковала все в новую красивую коробку, дала свою инструкцию по сборке и красивые декали от компании cartograf. Обилие облоя, не точностей и нестыковок обещает сделать сборку тем ещё приключением, но я давно хотел видеть в коллекции м1, так что будем стараться. #bmw #m1 #procar #mperformance #racing #car #124 #italeri #scale #scalemodel #scalemodelkit #hobby #art #standmodel #handmade #modeling

#sendology @european_vintage_cars Follow @sendology.101----------------------------------------1983 BMW M1 Le Mans car Team Warsteiner The BMW M1 was not only raced at the one-model Procar championship which supported the F1 races but also participated multiple years at the prestigious 24 hours of Le Mans endurance race.The BMW M1, Munich’s only mid-engined production car, competed at Le Mans over seven years from 1979 - 1986. During this time a total of twenty-two M1s qualified for the 24h race, with seven finishes and two class wins. With these modest results, the M1 could not find success at Le Mans which was due to two major reasons: Strong competition and poor reliability. The car seen in the photos was a sole M1 that participated in the 1983 race, the #90 Warsteiner entry. It performed quite well by qualifying first in class against several Porsche 930 turbos and 928’s. On track to win its class, the M1 made steady progress towards the front, despite losing nearly two and a half hours to repair bodywork and replace gearbox bolts. But the Sunday morning ended after 7:00 am when the gearbox failed. The car had climbed to 19th position overall.Along with a lack of power and poor reliability many problem areas afflicted M1s at Le Mans. Engine failures were common, resulting in the biggest number of retirements. An Achilles heel of the M1 engine was the crankshaft harmonic damper. Failure of this component occurred quite often, and not only led to downtime in the pits to replace the damper but also led to engine failure if the problem was not noticed early. Gearbox failures were common and the pit crew had to rebuild them quite often during the races. 1983 BMW M1 Le Mans car Team Warsteiner The BMW M1 was not only raced at the one-model Procar championship which supported the F1 races but also participated multiple years at the prestigious 24 hours of Le Mans endurance race.The BMW M1, Munich’s only mid-engined production car, competed at Le Mans over seven years from 1979 - 1986. During this time a total of twenty-two M1s qualified for the 24h race, with seven finishes and two class wins. With these modest results, the M1 could not find success at Le Mans which was due to two major reasons: Strong competition and poor reliability. The car seen in the photos was a sole M1 that participated in the 1983 race, the #90 Warsteiner entry. It performed quite well by qualifying first in class against several Porsche 930 turbos and 928’s. On track to win its class, the M1 made steady progress towards the front, despite losing nearly two and a half hours to repair bodywork and replace gearbox bolts. But the Sunday morning ended after 7:00 am when the gearbox failed. The car had climbed to 19th position overall.Along with a lack of power and poor reliability many problem areas afflicted M1s at Le Mans. Engine failures were common, resulting in the biggest number of retirements. An Achilles heel of the M1 engine was the crankshaft harmonic damper. Failure of this component occurred quite often, and not only led to downtime in the pits to replace the damper but also led to engine failure if the problem was not noticed early. Gearbox failures were common and the pit crew had to rebuild them quite often during the races.
